txt.en: Superb Warden's Shield of Lothlórien Scroll Case[E]
On opening, the scroll case will reveal the Superb Warden's Shield of Lothlórien recipe.\n\nYou must be friendly with the Galadhrim and Artisan of the Metalsmith's Guild to use this item.
